	<GeneDef ParentName="Outland_GeneHandsBase">
		<defName>Outland_Hands_VenomTalons</defName>
		<label>hands (venom talons)</label>
		<description>Carriers of this gene have sharp talons on the end of their fingers providing them sharp damage in melee combat. The talons naturally start excreting venom when adrenaline starts flowing, providing toxic damage when attacking.</description>
