	<GeneDef ParentName="Outland_GeneHandsBase">
		<defName>Outland_Hands_CrabClaw</defName>
		<label>hands (crab claw)</label>
		<description>Carriers of this gene have crab-like claws in place of hands. They can do massive damage in a fight but it makes them fairly useless outside of that.</description>
		<iconPath>Outland/GeneIcons/Gene_CrabHands</iconPath>
		<displayOrderInCategory>7805</displayOrderInCategory>
		<biostatMet>1</biostatMet>
		<customEffectDescriptions>
			<li>Adds hediffs to the pawns hands, giving a bonus attack which does increased sharp damage.</li>
