	<GeneDef ParentName="Outland_GeneHandsBase">
		<defName>Outland_Hands_RetractableBlades</defName>
		<label>hands (retractable blades)</label>
		<description>Carriers of this gene have retractable blades that extend from between the knucles. The ability to retract them keeps them out of the way and so doesn't have the debuff of reducing manipulation.</description>
		<iconPath>Outland/GeneIcons/Gene_RetractableBlades</iconPath>
		<displayOrderInCategory>7807</displayOrderInCategory>
		<biostatMet>-2</biostatMet>
		<customEffectDescriptions>
			<li>Adds hediffs to the pawns hands, giving a bonus attack which does sharp damage.</li>
			<li>Unlike other hand options which add a bonus attack, these do not have a manipulation debuff.</li>
		</customEffectDescriptions>
		<modExtensions>
			<li Class="VanillaGenesExpanded.GeneExtension">
				<backgroundPathEndogenes>Outland/GeneIcons/EndogeneBG</backgroundPathEndogenes>
				<backgroundPathXenogenes>Outland/GeneIcons/XenogeneBG</backgroundPathXenogenes>
